Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与地球的距离 3800
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.57,0:00:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用新型活性隐形系统
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.27,0:00:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲入大气层前不被发现的确率是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,58%
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我啊 GHOST！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上来把你变成废铁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作个了断吧 勇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.69,0:02:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SIS请通话…! 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回路正在被关系 第三 第四 第七无法运作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信回路无法运作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自动防卫系统被强行启动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续尝试直至线路回复正常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.68,0:02:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五级防卫状态?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是热烈的欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正没办法避开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有强行突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸毁卫星轨道上的自动防卫卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁它们的碎片冲人大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧起来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就混入那些碎片里冲下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:03:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候 为了不被识别出机体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要让操纵系统处于关闭状态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的程序所计算出的最佳方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这是最佳方法……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你的计算哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要信任我的技术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候和技术无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎是全靠运气的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运气也是技术的一部分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更加不能够信任呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是拥有生命的 在我的心里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对！你只是一个程序而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信自己有感情这件事也是虚构出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.25,0:04:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的拥有自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道自己要做什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能够自我思考
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有心 这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是由马捷虚构出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了实现我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才在这里活动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看他高兴的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…勇很快就会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 已经不再需要你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎朗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.39,0:06:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太完美了 莎朗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 用那光辉去照耀未来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来能赶得上约会的时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加鲁特?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来变成灰尘的应该是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴险的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是跟在别人背后打转
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没时间在这里跟你磨蹭！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是要妨碍我！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由小时候起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就总是跟在我背后打转
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人的屁股你也穷追不舍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元旦看日出时吃的鸡肉饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是我买的 但你却踢翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出脚的…是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想翻旧帐吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买的CTV
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到现在还没还给我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你七年前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己随便就丢掉的东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学的时候 我请你吃了两次午饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请了你十三次！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是记得很清楚啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的飞机弄坏的也是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼知道谁干的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟我装傻！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙总是要…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁掉我重要的东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我重要的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年前的那时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是你的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许…我什么都…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后 我把自己的记忆封闭了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.14,0:12:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了他吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为取回真正记忆的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在害怕…在痛苦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么认真啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候我们经常驾驶人力飞机玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关掉引擎 乘风翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还取名为『必杀气流上升』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道以前的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直被我骂做叛徒、卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美翁 她也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一起瞒着我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在可怜我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.41,0:14:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄坏了你做的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想试着飞一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是过去的事了 忘记它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:14:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个让人讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 感情很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌声?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GHOST吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 终于遇上它了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 起床了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:15:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加鲁特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的约会对像 你别出手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的台词！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌声…难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你们 帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『勇』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是莎朗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连MACROSS的主电脑都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西在说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她完全暴走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GHOST也是被莎朗所操纵的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等你 勇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美翁! 美翁呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的她只是一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌和爱情她已经交托给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的脑内一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什么！你对美翁做了什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有人能分开我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物由我来对付
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去美翁那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加鲁特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是你和这家伙战斗的时候！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时都要保护美翁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们的誓言吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美翁在等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 你一定要把她带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你无法打败GHOST！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样做或许更明智
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连你都说这种话…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要磨磨蹭蹭的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！无论谁都是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后可别哀求我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MACROSS…在动！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像记起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样接近会有危险的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.66,0:21:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是陷阱…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收声! 正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.77,0:21:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心底的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你藏起来的一切感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是莎朗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎朗把MACROSS占据了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.80,0:22:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要阻止莎朗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.74,0:22:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要破坏MACROSS的中枢情报网络！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.88,0:22:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心脏部份在…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇已经是我的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了! 要害在主天线后面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.40,0:22:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正下方13D
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.98,0:23:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是勇吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.62,0:23:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美翁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.75,0:23:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.46,0:23:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.51,0:23:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.11,0:23:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把病毒…输入莎朗的网络
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.75,0:23:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她产生混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得到吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.62,0:23:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是多余的问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.04,0:23:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.85,0:23:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下来啊！求求你！停下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.12,0:23:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有人能够阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.96,0:23:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:23:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来阻止给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.11,0:24:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.14,0:24:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.95,0:24:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你所希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.36,0:24:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感动
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.23,0:24:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给予这世上每一个人应有的感动
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.40,0:25:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现爱人的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.74,0:25:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他最大的感动
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.27,0:25:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得『那就是我活着的证明』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.02,0:25:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有…?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.95,0:25:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么…?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.75,0:25:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种无聊的感动 无论哪里都没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.80,0:25:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇所寻求的是遥远的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.23,0:25:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命挑战天空时
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.20,0:25:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在生与死的狭间
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.00,0:25:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窥见的感动
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.57,0:25:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是希望勇能感受到那种感动
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.75,0:25:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么也别做
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.79,0:26:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.96,0:26:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.41,0:26:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.68,0:26:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有解除限制器发挥极限性能
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.12,0:26:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇 情况怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.59,0:26:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加鲁特吗? 很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.60,0:26:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到美翁了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.06,0:26:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.97,0:26:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有告诉她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.11,0:26:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.74,0:26:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很快就能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.78,0:26:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待与你痛饮一场
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.96,0:26:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.05,0:27:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆祝我们七年后久别重逢 干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.82,0:27:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我先行一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.16,0:27:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加鲁特
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.60,0:27:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加鲁特…加鲁特！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.97,0:27:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『危险临界点』
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.95,0:27:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.13,0:27:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快…就能…连接上莎朗了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.54,0:28:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杨
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.91,0:28:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.25,0:28:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 连杨都…！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.63,0:29:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了! 我不想听你的怪歌声！
